PIENAAR –  Police made a  gruesome discovery when they dug up the decomposed body of a three-year old-girl buried in a shallow grave. Police spokesman Col Mtsholi Bhembe said they had  received information about a child which was reportedly murdered in 2015, and buried in a shallow grave, within the yard of a house in Gobhoza Section. “As a result , the police are looking for the father of the victim known as Phanuel Kombora and the step-mother known only as Francis, we believe may be able to assist in the investigation of this matter.” An appeal is also made to anyone who may have information on the couple’s whereabouts to contact Lt Col Jackie Mbuyane 082 469 1478 or the SAPS Crime Line 08600 10111.